data.description: Luxurious, private, spacious & open. 12 ft ceilings, walls of windows & natural light. Whole house generator, on-demand water heater, 3-car garage! Chef's kitchen w/quality stainless appliances, gas cook-top, spacious walk-in pantry. Kitchen flows into dining area & great room w/fireplace (BEAUTIFUL view.) Airy 1st floor owner's suite, zero-entry shower, huge closet, steps from laundry (NICE). 1st flr home office. Finished LL w/3 egress windows, large windows, bright lighting. Sprawling rec room, wet bar, second bedroom, full bath, half bath & flex space. Add'l storage in LL utility rm. Park 3 cars in heated tandem  w/hot &cold water. Serene patio community.  In OH's most beautiful Olentangy River region w/fast access to downtown, freeways, and conveniences. Priced well below comparables.
